companyName: First Trust NASDAQ ABA Community Bank Index Fund
description:
The investment seeks investment results that correspond generally to the price and yield (before the fund's fees and expenses) of an equity index called the NASDAQ OMX® ABA Community Bank IndexSM.
 The fund will normally invest at least 90% of its net assets (including investment borrowings) in common stocks that comprise the index. The index is a market-capitalization-weighted index.
